title: Poovarasam Peepee
subTitle: Three young boys witness a gruesome murder during their summer holidays. Later, they take it upon themselves to find and punish the culprits.

title: Oru Thaai Makkal
subTitle: A rich man adopts one of the twin sons of his maid after his own child dies. However, fate brings the brothers face to face when they both fall in love with the same woman.

title: Jannal Oram

title: Panchalankurichi

title: Maragatha Veenai

title: Asuran
subTitle: Amidst the chaos of a criminal constantly evading the police and a woman's love affair with an agricultural officer, something sinister brews that affects everyone's life.

title: Veetula Raman Veliyila Krishnan
subTitle: Rajasekaran, a civil engineer, marries Jayalakshmi and moves to the city. Their peaceful life turns chaotic when their neighbour Subba Rao casts an evil eye on Jayalakshmi.
